text:
childhood favorite chicken rice! $3 is SUPER affordable, please patronise this stall! they hasn't increase their prices for so long.

chilli is also really good, paired really well with their rice.

chicken is quite tender and not dry!

stall lady is also friendly ☺️
friendly auntie and uncle that charges only 3$ even after covid and inflation!! they are super trustworthy of their customers too. pls go and support if you’re nearby!
